title: filetopiafx.file-server.sharing.P2P.network.client
description:
Brand new edition of Filetopia!!! P2P file-sharing network 

-Access media File-Servers from users across the globe.  
-Find files on different file-servers all connected to the same network.
-Share your own data with a group of friends or meet new peers.
-Find hard to access media in various formats that may not be torrents.
-Average File-Server user has 5TB or more of data
-Join chat rooms where users can discuss downloading/uploading files to each other.
-Make your own public or private sharing rooms or Join existing ones on the network.
-Filetopiafx is an upgrade from the 2002 version that started the P2P industry 

-Install filetopia(32bit) and begin satisfying all of your downloading desires with millions of files spread across hundreds of users. 

-DOWNLOAD ANY FILE YOU WANT THAT IS LOCATED ON THE NETWORK FOR FREE!!!!!!!!!!
